<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Using_.24headers_To_Set_.22From:.22.2C_.22Cc:.22_and_.22Bcc:.22_Parameters"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Using $headers To Set "From:", "Cc:" and "Bcc:" Parameters</span></a></li>
